      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface wear and a few small stone chips consistent with normal driving, while the interior remains in great shape with some slight creasing on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. You can expect a reliable ride that shows pride of ownership despite its minor age-related imperfections.",
