      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered, always garage-kept, and the interior is still spotless. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new, you've found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 44900.0,
