    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear, high-revving power band. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated shells, the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisans components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, with no bushing deflection or fluid seepage. Finished in Alpine White over an immaculate Nappa leather interior, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
